        {
          "insert": "projectToMarkdown",
          "attributes": {
            "code": true
          }
        },
        {
          "insert": ". The function is pure and runtime-only: it never writes a markdown mirror to disk, so the projection can never go stale against the source of truth. Each block type has a deterministic, greppable form, produced by the owning component's "
        },
